AB Patent analysis is a particularly promising avenue for further research
   and development. Although patent analysis has a long history, there is
   a rapidly increase interest in incorporating information visualization
   and especially knowledge domain visualization techniques into the
   patent analysis practice. In this paper, we describe an application of
   knowledge domain visualization techniques to the domain of patent
   citation analysis as our first step to identify the salient structure
   of this evolving knowledge domain.
